{"tid":1666900,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中聯辦係咪無人負責同伊斯蘭領袖聯絡？","createTime":"2019-10-21T07:33:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T02:00:08.000Z","uid":228995,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"32442bbe72f84197d5c54f545a524eab5aa472f2","tid":1666900,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:33:32.000Z","msg":"報紙成日話香港有六大宗教領袖<br />\n咁一定包伊斯蘭教啦<br />\n我再search 下香港伊斯蘭教邊個做領袖<br />\n<br />\n原來係有個叫中華回教博愛社<br />\n係&rdquo;華人穆斯林社團&rdquo;<br />\n主席叫薩智生<br />\n特首選委有成10席<br />\n<br />\n但另一方面<br />\n來自南亞嘅伊斯蘭教朋友<br />\n係一席都無<br />\n<br />\n其實好多南亞朋友都係香港長大<br />\n如果香港人connect對方<br />\n一定係雙贏局面"},{"pid":"4772fa87ca4a0238a0bbc791d6ef7bdd798fa3bf","tid":1666900,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:33:38.000Z","msg":"不如全港黨鐵靜坐聲討721啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1665580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1665580</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"997fdbf1cb490623065247aff19d2cd1e824a153","tid":1666900,"uid":265168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:34:34.000Z","msg":"屌晒你地<br />\n尋晚開行動po到而家都仲未上到熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢單野新鮮滾熱辣 connect全世界<br />\n依家就係最好時機！<br />\n<br />\n我地fight for freedom<br />\n我無宗教信仰 但我有宗教自由 <br />\n<br />\n早喺六月已經有宗教俾popo當眾侮辱 <br />\n打壓宗教自由之餘亦都對各個宗教不尊重<br />\n<br />\n睇原po！<br />\n既然我哋係fight for freedom<br />\n咁我哋更加係時候聲援被打壓宗教自由嘅人！<br />\n快啲一齊討論！<br />\n<br />\n係時候搞個 尊重宗教自由大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1665685\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1665685</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"eadaa17a5577fd6db96e3403fbedf2c65ba86fc9","tid":1666900,"uid":322622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:37:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3a5b4695037db19908a5b9df6cf51b5a12334a9d","tid":1666900,"uid":292267,"like":0,"dislik